# Project Structure Overview

- **Frontend root**: `src/`
  - `app/` – API route handlers (serverless/edge functions) + utils
      - Nested folders hold specific route handlers (`api/ai`, `api/uploadthing`)
  - `components/` – React UI components
      - `editor/` – Plate-based rich-text editor and plugin kits
      - `ui/` – Small reusable UI components built on Radix & Tailwind
  - `hooks/` – Custom React hooks
  - `lib/` – Shared utilities (`uploadthing.ts`, `utils.ts`)
  - `pages/` – Top-level route components (e.g. `Editor.tsx`)
  - `assets/` – Static assets used by React
- **Desktop target**: `src-tauri/` – Rust + Tauri backend, packaged via `tauri.conf.json`
- **Styling**
  - TailwindCSS 3.x with variables & dark-mode class (`src/index.css`, `tailwind.config.js`)
- **Build & Tooling**
  - Vite 5 config in `vite.config.ts`
  - Absolute import alias: `@` → `src/`

Keep this directory map in sync when moving or renaming folders.
